9Z9qdg">Tuý hoa âm - Độc cựu thi - 醉花蔭－讀舊詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-T%E1%BB%B1-Thanh/author-wQICzKRVau8PqmJ28C9K6g">Cao Tự Thanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-T%E1%BA%AFc-T%E1%BB%AB/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-xu%E1%BA%A5t-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Quan-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-Gi%E1%BA%A3i-Qu%C3%A2n-ti%E1%BB%81n-b%E1%BB%91i-t%E1%BB%B1-Y-L%C3%AA-lai-th%C6%B0-ph%C3%BA-th%E1%BB%AD-kh%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-k%C3%BD-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-X9RoLtVOrpnvsp4HJY_FsQ">Tương xuất Ngọc Quan đắc Giải Quân tiền bối tự Y Lê lai thư phú thử khước ký kỳ 2 - 將出玉關得嶰筠前輩自伊犁來書賦此卻寄其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-T%E1%BA%AFc-T%E1%BB%AB/author-JAv5RkZakjKTfe65gwrmsQ">Lâm Tắc Từ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Vi%E1%BB%87t-nh%C3%A2n-ca/poem-7GhgUX-NtPQ9F4NqWEt47A">Việt nhân ca - 越人歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Xu%C3%A2n-d%E1%BA%A1-Gi%C3%A1p-Ch%C3%A2u-%C4%90i%E1%BB%81n-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-s%E1%BB%AD-Lu%E1%BA%ADt-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-l%C6%B0u-y%E1%BA%BFn-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-di%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-kIOYuHz4tz1LCS_dEKbcsg">Xuân dạ Giáp Châu Điền thị ngự trưởng sử Luật Đình lưu yến, đắc diên tự - 春夜峽州田侍禦長史津亭留宴，得筵字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
